{"tid":2442663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位運動員準備好打支那疫苗未","createTime":"2021-03-11T13:16:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T13:21:25.000Z","uid":133743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e422875e1fabdf922b6c946eae979b7d00f6b482","tid":2442663,"uid":133743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:16:16.000Z","msg":"原文：<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20210311/A4GLOQN3YRHNVLZ4VMOXWILD5Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20210311%2FA4GLOQN3YRHNVLZ4VMOXWILD5Y%2F&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHfUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=d8bc39e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20210311%2FA4GLOQN3YRHNVLZ4VMOXWILD5Y%2F&h=8bfeb682\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20210311/A4GLOQN3YRHNVLZ4VMOXWILD5Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n國際奧委會為東京奧運及北京冬奧參與者提供國產疫苗<br />\n<br />\n周四國際奧委會（IOC）會長巴赫宣佈，中國奧委會已經提議為今年東京奧運以及2022年北京冬季奧運會的所有參與者，即連同所有工作人員在內，為他們提供中國製疫苗，而且IOC將會負責支付這些中國製疫苗的費用。"},{"pid":"3be6515ebd0194b560eb0a92fce824fdee2a957f","tid":2442663,"uid":133743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:17:03.000Z","msg":"運動員應該冇糖尿病同高血壓"},{"pid":"a4651d2ec6a21e2f44e724aa7fe20a053ede6b8e","tid":2442663,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:20:25.000Z","msg":"你支冬會搞得成先算啦"},{"pid":"8dcee73f0740002429b47651115c8ff402566153","tid":2442663,"uid":133743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a4651d2ec6a21e2f44e724aa7fe20a053ede6b8e","tid":2442663,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:20:25.000Z","msg":"你支冬會搞得成先算啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:21:25.000Z","msg":"2022年仲要打疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}